<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>About SNGCE Hostels</title>
  <script src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com"></script>
</head>
<body>
  <!-- Background Section -->
  <div class="w-full min-h-screen bg-[url('images/resize.png')] bg-no-repeat bg-cover bg-center px-6 sm:px-12 py-10 relative">

    <!-- Overlay for readability -->
    <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-black bg-opacity-60"></div>

    <!-- Content Section -->
    <div class="relative z-10 max-w-4xl mx-auto text-white bg-black bg-opacity-50 p-8 rounded-2xl shadow-lg">
      <h1 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-bold text-pink-400 mb-6 text-center">
        About SNGCE Hostels
      </h1>

      <p class="mb-4 leading-relaxed">
        SNGCE has fully furnished separate in-campus Gents and Ladies Hostels. 
        Gents hostel is situated behind the college within the campus. 
        The ladies hostel is located on the front side of the college. 
        Both hostels provide calm and conducive ambience to develop the inherent abilities of inmates. 
        Indoor and outdoor facilities for sports and cultural activities are available in both the hostels.
      </p>

      <p class="mb-4 leading-relaxed">
        The gents’ hostel can accommodate <span class="font-semibold text-pink-300">240 inmates</span>. 
        The ladies hostel can accommodate <span class="font-semibold text-pink-300">400 inmates</span>. 
        The gents’ hostel is under the control of the full-time Warden, assisted by the Hostel Manager and 
        ladies hostel is under the control of the full-time Warden assisted by two Matrons.
      </p>

      <p class="mb-4 leading-relaxed">
        The hostel mess is run by the mess committee elected by the students. 
        A sterile atmosphere is available in the hostels. House-keeping in charges look after the hostels 
        and maintain a diplomatic, hygienic and mesmerizing environment in the hostels. 
        A medical clinic functions in the main academic block with a doctor during all working days. 
        <span class="font-semibold text-pink-300">24hrs ambulance service</span> is also available in the college campus including hostels.
      </p>

      <p class="mb-4 leading-relaxed">
        Hostel day (<span class="italic">MH day and LH day</span>) celebrations are conducted in both hostels with the 
        active participation of inmates, management, faculty and staff of the college.
      </p>

      <!-- Button -->
      <div class="text-center mt-8">
        <a href="/" 
           class="px-6 py-3 bg-pink-500 text-white rounded-xl shadow-md hover:bg-pink-600 transition">
          Back to Home
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
